snippet.title: Teddison Inc Trailer
snippet.description:
Teddison Inc is a relaxing incremental/idle game for the Playdate! Start out in a dusty warehouse with a bike and a dream. Then build your electricity empire to take over the world!
Get it now on itch.io! https://mirrordoor.itch.io/teddison-inc

Please consider leaving a comment or a review!  I would really appreciate your feedback!
